## Private Member Attributes

### AuthPtrStubs {#ae762b676bdc131bd636e89de8c118dae}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>DenseMap&lt;MCSymbol &#42;, const MCExpr &#42;&gt; llvm::MachineModuleInfoMachO::AuthPtrStubs</>}>
Darwin &#39;$auth&#95;ptr&#39; stubs.

The key is the stub symbol, like &quot;Lfoo$auth&#95;ptr$ib$12&quot;. The value is the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcexpr">MCExpr</a> representing that signed pointer, something like &quot;&#95;foo@AUTH(ib, 12)&quot;.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/machinemoduleinfoimpls-h/#l00042">42</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/machinemoduleinfoimpls-h">MachineModuleInfoImpls.h</a>.

### GVStubs {#a8afb8429f8ceca25f2fec8868a49662e}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>DenseMap&lt;MCSymbol &#42;, StubValueTy&gt; llvm::MachineModuleInfoMachO::GVStubs</>}>
GVStubs - Darwin &#39;$non&#95;lazy&#95;ptr&#39; stubs.

The key is something like &quot;Lfoo$non&#95;lazy&#95;ptr&quot;, the value is something like &quot;&#95;foo&quot;. The extra bit is true if this GV is external.
